
# Privacy Policy

## Introduction
This Privacy Policy describes how data is collected, used, and handled in the Goa Assembly Elections 2022 Facebook research project.

## Data Collected
This project collects only:
- Public Facebook Page posts
- Page names
- Post text
- Post timestamps
- Public permalinks

No personal user data, private profiles, messages, or non-public information is accessed or stored.

## Purpose of Data Collection
Data is collected solely for:
- Academic research
- Network analysis of political communication
- Replication and validation of existing scholarly literature

## Data Storage and Security
- Data is stored locally in CSV format
- No data is shared with third parties
- Data is not sold, monetized, or used for advertising

## User Privacy
This project does not track individuals or attempt to identify users. All analysis is conducted at the Page or aggregate textual level.

## Contact
For questions regarding this policy, contact the repository maintainer via GitHub.

